dataset.name: ds
dataset.sql: select tei.entryid,tei.filingyear,tcl.classname,tcl.codelevel,tei.funds,tfs.fundsname, tei.entryretention,tei.filedate from tb_entry_index tei LEFT JOIN tb_data_node tdn on tei.nodeid = tdn.nodeid LEFT JOIN tb_classification tcl on tdn.classid = tcl.classid LEFT JOIN tb_funds tfs on tei.funds = tfs.funds where tei.funds is not null and tei.funds != ''
